Interface HairDryerOperationI

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    HairDryerElectricityModel, HairDryerStateModel, HairDryerUserModel

    public interface HairDryerOperationI
    The interface HairDryerOperationI declares operations that simulation models must implement to have events associated with the models execute on them.
